title: CCENT2 - CCNA Intro - Packet Tracer app and Lessons
description:
Included here are the Packet Tracer lessons and labs from Cisco Net Academy - CCENT - Module 2 (Class 2)

If you sign up for the class, you get the online instruction, which includes a walk-through with slides and videos, even a large book, and we meet twice a week with an instructor, which of course aren't included here. This zip file is only the packet tracer app, the packet tracer lessons and lab sheets from the website. If you are planning on earning your CCNA or just the CCENT, I encourage you to enroll in a class, in person or brick-and-mortar. Lots of activities and lessons, even a subnetting worksheet.

This package is also useful/helpful for anyone interested in Network+.

Directory of Folders:

CCNA 2 - Labs
CCNA 2 - Packet Tracer Lessons
